# 9point75 Woodworks LLC – Website Build Roadmap
**Platform:** HTML/CSS/JS (Cursor + Codex)  
**Hosting:** GitHub → Vercel (free)  
**Domain:** Cloudflare → Vercel  
**Launch Target:** April 30, 2026  
**Budget:** $0 additional spend  
**Builder:** Solo (you + Codex)

## Phase 0: Setup & Foundation (Mar 23 – Mar 25)
**Objective:** Create a clean repo and dev environment that supports fast, repeatable deploys.

**Deliverables:**
- GitHub repository initialized with proper structure
- Vercel project connected and auto-deploying from main branch
- Basic folder structure and starter files
- Cloudflare domain DNS documentation saved
- README.md with build & deploy instructions

**Dependencies:** None

## Phase 1: Design System & Core Structure (Mar 26 – Apr 1)
**Objective:** Build a consistent, handcrafted design system and page skeleton.

**Deliverables:**
- Tailwind CSS via CDN (or clean custom CSS) implemented
- Typography scale, color palette, spacing system defined
- Reusable components: sticky header, footer, buttons, cards
- Mobile-first responsive layout foundation
- All 4 pages created with placeholder content

**Dependencies:** Phase 0 complete

## Phase 2: Homepage Build (Apr 2 – Apr 8)
**Objective:** Complete homepage that matches the wireframe and strongly drives quote requests.

**Deliverables:**
- Hero section (text-driven)
- Value Proposition (3 columns)
- How It Works (step layout)
- Featured Work image grid (6–9 items)
- Materials / Craftsmanship section
- Trust Signals section
- Subtle CTAs throughout
- Navigation fully wired

**Dependencies:** Phase 1 complete

## Phase 3: Supporting Pages (Apr 9 – Apr 15)
**Objective:** Build Gallery, About, and Contact/Quote pages.

**Deliverables:**
- Gallery page with category filters + vanilla JS lightbox
- About page with personal story and philosophy
- Contact/Quote page with full form
- Consistent navigation and footer across all pages

**Dependencies:** Phase 2 complete

## Phase 4: Content Integration & Polish (Apr 16 – Apr 22)
**Objective:** Replace placeholders with real optimized content and photos.

**Deliverables:**
- All real photos curated, compressed, and inserted with alt text
- Final copy written and integrated on every page
- Form fully functional and tested
- Performance optimizations applied
- Accessibility basics completed

**Dependencies:** Phase 3 complete

## Phase 5: Testing, SEO & Launch (Apr 23 – Apr 30)
**Objective:** Bug-free, professional site live on custom domain.

**Deliverables:**
- Full manual + device testing completed
- Basic SEO (meta tags, headings, alt text, Open Graph)
- Cloudflare domain pointed to Vercel + SSL active
- Lighthouse scores ≥ 90 where possible
- Final launch checklist signed off

**Dependencies:** Phase 4 complete